# Test 14: Factorial function
Create a function called factorial that takes n:
    If n is less than 2, then:
        Return 1.
    End if.
    Set result to 1.
    For i from 2 to n, do:
        Set result to result times i.
    End for.
    Return result.
End function.

Show "Factorials:".
For i from 1 to 10, do:
    Set f to call factorial with i.
    Show i plus "! = " plus f.
End for.
